result.formatted_address: H8, 8 Hau Fook St, Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong
result.name: Outdark Korean Restaurant辣炒春雞

reviews.text:
I've never had a bad experience at outdark and this time was no different. Their food is ways good, you really can't go wrong with anything from the menu. 

Their ambience is also worth noting. It's very rare you have a place where the music isn't too overbearing and yet nothing feels quiet in a bad way, I think mainly because you can have a decent conversation.

If you come remember to ask for a lock to out on their fence, or at least wrote yourself a postcard, the restaurant will actually send it out to you. I know cuz i tried a few times. Definitely fun.
It’s still good even the Korean craze has died down, hipsters hangout for fried chicken and a few drinks...

Good fried chicken with a lot of varieties of fries! Love the honey flavor!!!! They are pretty famous for the cheesy ribs but i like the fried chicken more. We also ordered the rice with seaweed, personally i think it is standard. The price without the ribs is okay... but quite expensive for the ribs with that quality. :) oh rite. 1,5 hour per seating. And they will give you a polaroid photo if you eat with them during birthday.
One of the best Korean restaurant in HK. Casual  place for local younsters.

Cheese pork rib is pretty awesome here. I love their hand-made rice ball idea. When you enter the restaurant, you will see those couple locks on the right, and in front, there is a mail box, with some postcards on the side. You can write a post card to yourself or friends. I think it is like $5 per post card? Will definitely recommend this restaurant to people who love Korean food!

result.name: Outdark Korean Restaurant 辣炒春雞

reviews.text:
🙌🏻人頭湧湧的韓式炸雞店

尖沙咀分店人流特別多，加上餐廳沒有訂位服務，所以需要等候10分鐘或以上了，建議大家早一點來排隊😌。🤩在排隊的過程中，大家可以先拍照📷，拍下這浪漫燈光下的氛圍✨。

🍴海鮮奶油年糕 ($298)
Seafood Cream Ddeok-bokki
點了一個賣相澎湃的海鮮盤，海鮮包括一隻炸魷魚🦑、蜆及蝦🦐。影相後，店員會幫忙把魷魚剪開✂️，魷魚經過脆炸，乾身又惹味，十分香口。鍋中間的忌廉汁香濃，配上吸了味的椰菜和年糕，味道不錯👍🏻。鐵鍋旁邊還有菠蘿🍍、紫菜飯和芝士🧀。芝士鹹香軟滑，十分好吃，整個海鮮鐵鍋十分豐富，份量足夠3-4人分享😋👍🏻。
建議大家年糕要煮耐一點才吃，因為年糕要點時間煮腍至入味，到時口感和味道都會更好呢🤘🏻。
.
🍴東萊海鮮煎餅 ($118)
Dongrae Seafood Jijim
煎餅以大蔥做底，加入魷魚🦑、蝦肉🦐等配料，煎至香口，蔥香味尤其突出，而且厚薄適中，味道不錯，但價錢略為進取。

今晚約左另一半食韓國🇰🇷嘢，大家講明一定要炸雞🍗啤酒🍻，研究左一輪，終於決定去尖沙咀Outdark🤗一出電梯門，一幅巨型嘅情人鎖🔒牆已經非常吸引我，成千上萬的情人鎖，代表著無限的愛💕意，未坐低已經甜到漏😍環境氣氛可以話好Romantic，特別係天花掛滿了星星🌟，好有氣氛，原來係配合Outdark個Dark字，比一般餐廳高的桌椅坐得好舒服，傾計都特別開懷🤗客人仲可以免費為自己寄出未來的信，好有賣點，我都唔客氣將心聲一一記下，期待收到時願望是否成真🌟餐牌設計像報紙📰，還特別介紹餐廳歷史和名字起源，很有心思👍🏻乜都唔使講，先來一份香蒜蜜糖炸雞🍗$178，份量之大，不禁令我們嘩的一聲，大大件炸雞為數不少，應該起碼超過十件，而且啖啖肉無骨，蜜糖甜甜的，雞皮又脆卜卜，而且肉香嫰滑，而家諗返都流口水，再加埋4⃣️種醬汁，令食雞嘅味道層次有不同享受👍🏻好味指數💡💡💡💡💡爆燈海鮮炒粉絲$98，配料新鮮，韓國餐廳來講呢間算做得好味，尤其蜆同蝦肉都feel到唔係雪藏嘢，粉絲都好入味，不錯👍🏻東萊海鮮煎餅$118，呢個雖然叫煎餅，但食落一啲都唔油膩，配料有好多蔬菜，切開左一件件四方形，方便易食😋
食下炸雞🍗飲下啤酒🍻，零捨Relax，韓籍侍應招呼周到，還替我們拍照📷留念，給我們留下美好回憶，很不錯的一個晚上😍

訂位會好一些，尖沙咀人流旺
暗暗環境浪漫，韓流音樂

炸雞好食配菜炸薯條仍要改善，薯格好食
，炸八爪魚 好食
海鮮年糕窩 材料十足
環境不俗。海鮮蔥餅超級有驚喜。Delicious 😋😋

I've never had a bad experience at outdark and this time was no different. Their food is ways good, you really can't go wrong with anything from the menu. 

Their ambience is also worth noting. It's very rare you have a place where the music isn't too overbearing and yet nothing feels quiet in a bad way, I think mainly because you can have a decent conversation.

If you come remember to ask for a lock to out on their fence, or at least wrote yourself a postcard, the restaurant will actually send it out to you. I know cuz i tried a few times. Definitely fun.
